{"code":"ECONNABORTED","config":{"adapter":["xhr","http","fetch"],"allowAbsoluteUrls":true,"data":"{\"model\":\"z-ai/glm4.7\",\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"\\n作为专业的股票技术分析师，请分析以下股票数据：\\n\\n股票代码: NVDA\\n当前价格: 186.94 USD\\n涨跌幅: -1.61%\\n今日最高: 193.6 USD\\n今日最低: 186.51 USD\\n成交量: N/A\\n\\n技术指标:\\n- SMA20: 185.52\\n- SMA50: 184.38\\n- RSI(14): 29.41\\n- MACD: 0.38\\n- 布林带: 上轨196.36 | 中轨185.52 | 下轨174.68\\n\\n请从以下几个维度进行专业分析：\\n\\n1. **价格走势分析**：分析当前价格相对于技术指标的位置\\n2. **技术指标信号**：解读RSI、MACD、均线等指标释放的信号  \\n3. **支撑阻力位**：识别关键的支撑位和阻力位\\n4. **成交量分析**：结合成交量分析价格走势的可靠性\\n5. **短期预测**：基于技术面给出1-3个交易日的走势预判\\n6. **交易建议**：给出明确的买入/持有/卖出建议，包括目标价位和止损位\\n\\n请用专业、客观的语言给出分析结论，控制在400字以内。\\n\"}],\"max_tokens\":4000,\"temperature\":0.7}","env":{},"headers":{"Accept":"application/json, text/plain, */*","Accept-Encoding":"gzip, compress, deflate, br","Authorization":"Bearer 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","Content-Length":"1045","Content-Type":"application/json","User-Agent":"axios/1.13.5"},"maxBodyLength":-1,"maxContentLength":-1,"method":"post","timeout":60000,"transformRequest":[null],"transformResponse":[null],"transitional":{"clarifyTimeoutError":false,"forcedJSONParsing":true,"legacyInterceptorReqResOrdering":true,"silentJSONParsing":true},"url":"https://integrate.api.nvidia.com/v1/chat/completions","xsrfCookieName":"XSRF-TOKEN","xsrfHeaderName":"X-XSRF-TOKEN"},"isAxiosError":true,"level":"error","message":"Analysis API error: timeout of 60000ms exceeded","name":"AxiosError","request":{"_currentRequest":{"_closed":false,"_contentLength":1045,"_defaultKeepAlive":true,"_ended":false,"_events":{},"_eventsCount":2,"_hasBody":true,"_header":"POST /v1/chat/completions HTTP/1.1\r\nAccept: application/json, text/plain, */*\r\nContent-Type: application/json\r\nAuthorization: Bearer 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\r\nUser-Agent: axios/1.13.5\r\nContent-Length: 1045\r\nAccept-Encoding: gzip, compress, deflate, b